 play a Troll or an Evil Smurf. She likes pretty characters. It's a girl thing.<br><br>So, what do you think? What class would be *your* skald's perfect Dream Date? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/ugelainsidhe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gelain Sidhe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#ff0000>(5/3/02 3:55:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=40.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Best duo partner for a Skald?</span><hr size=1> Actually some o' the female smurfs look quite cute.  <p><img src=http://home.cox.rr.com/junix/DAoCpics/Gelain25.jpg></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#efe0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/udaocobserver.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DAoC Observer</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#ff0000>(5/3/02 5:24:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=40.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Best duo partner for a Skald?</span><hr size=1> I tried that angle, no dice. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Skald/Healer? Skald/Thane? Skald/Hunter? If you were some pansy from Albion, what combo would make *you* wet your skirt?<br><br>(Yes, I do play characters in all three realms, you don't have to defend the skirts.) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/usteelv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SteelV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Member</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#ff0000>(5/3/02 7:05:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=40.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://216.66.10.138/alacrityface_pic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Best duo partner for a Skald?</span><hr size=1> Well at like level 40 you guys would be killing oranges pretty quickly if it was skald/thane, but a healer could be really nice also... hard choice. <p><table width="533" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">  <tr>     <td width="32" rowspan="4"><img src="http://216.66.10.138/alacrityface_pic.jpg"></td>    <td width="495">       <div align="center"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#999999" size="1">Midgard/Iseult</font></div>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>     <td width="495">       <div align="center"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#FF0000" size="1">Alacrity         | GM - <a href="http://216.66.10.138/sv">Steel Vengeance</a> | [38 Skald]</font></div>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>     <td width="495">       <div align="center"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#999999" size="1">Dwaslain         Wanderer | Officer - <a href="http://216.66.10.138/ddc">Dwa Dwarf Clan</a>|         [38 Zerk]</font></div>    </td>  </tr>  <tr>     <td width="495">       <div align="center"><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#999999" size="1">Erus         Morte| <a href="http://gstorm.iwarp.com" target="_blank">Eternal Storm</a>|         [20 SM]</font></div>    </td>  </tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#efe0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20